Method Detail

toString

public java.lang.String toString()
Returns a String object representing this TypeScope's value.

If this object represents the item type scope, a string equal to "ITEM" is returned.

If this object represents the request type scope, a string equal to "REQUEST" is returned.

If this object represents the baseline type scope, a string equal to "BASELINE" is returned.

If this object represents the design part type scope, a string equal to "DESIGN PART" is returned.

If this object represents the project scope, a string equal to "PROJECT" is returned.

If this object represents the user type scope, a string equal to "USER" is returned.
